thread.title: Marte's homer in 12th inning lifts Pirates over Reds 6-4
thread.title_full: Marte's homer in 12th inning lifts Pirates over Reds 6-4

title: Marte's homer in 12th inning lifts Pirates over Reds 6-4
text:
> Ohio Marte's homer in 12th inning lifts Pirates over Reds 6-4 CORRECTS TO TWELVE INNINGS-Pittsburgh Pirates' Starling Marte, right, is doused with water by teammates as the celebrate as Marte comes to home plate after hitting a two-run walk off game winning home run in the 12th inning of a baseball game against the Cincinnati Reds, Friday, Oct. 2, 2015, in Pittsburgh. The Pirates won 6-4 in twelve innings. (AP Photo/Keith Srakocic)
